am Tighe|title=Statistical observations relative to the county of Kilkenny: made in the years 1800 & 1801|date=1802|publisher=Printed by Graisberry and Campbell|url=https://books.google.ie/books?id=iTBWAAAAYAAJ|language=en|ref=harv}}\n<!-- End Sources -->\n{{Refend}}\n\n==External links==\n\n* {{cite web|last1=Walsh|first1=Dennis|title=Barony of Galmoy|url=http://sites.rootsweb.com/~irlkik/history/galmoy.htm|website=ancestry.com}}\n* {{cite web|title=Barony of Galmoy, Co. Kilkenny|url=https://www.townlands.ie/kilkenny/galmoy2/|website=townlands.ie}}\n* {{cite web|author=Fiontar|title=Barony of Gabhalmhaigh/Galmoy|url=http://www.logainm.ie/en/120 |website=logainm.ie|publisher=Department of Community, Rural and Gaeltacht Affairs of the Government of Ireland|date=2008|ref=harv}}\n\n{{Kilkenny-baronies}}\n\n[[Category:Baronies of County Kilkenny|Galmoy]]\n", "name_user": "Grant65", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Galmoy_(barony)"}
